## Testing

The generated server includes **three layers** of tests:

### Run All Tests

```bash
npm test
```

### Test Layers

| Layer | Location | Command | Description |
| ----- | -------- | ------- | ----------- |
| **Route tests** | `__tests__/routes/` | `npm run test:routes` | Supertest integration tests for all CRUD endpoints |
| **Service tests** | `__tests__/services/` | `npm run test:services` | Unit tests for in-memory service layer |
| **Contextual tests** | `contextual-tests/` | `npm run test:contextual` | AI-generated schema-aware business scenario tests |

